---
title: Chipotle Rice Bowls with Beyond Meat®  and Rainbow Toppings
description: Who doesn't love a hearty, plant-based meal full of southwestern flavour? This one features Beyond Meat® sautéed with sweet corn, as well as fresh tomato, tangy pickled cabbage and a zingy chipotle-ranch drizzle.
